casebody.data:
Shailer, Appellant, v. Morgan, Respondent. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. November 17, 1890.) Appeal from eleventh district court.

Argued before Daly, C. J., and Bischoff and Pryor, JJ.

Hatch & Warren, for appellant. E. C. O’Brien, for respondent.

No opinion. Judgment reversed, new trial ordered, costs to abide the event. See 9 N. Y. Supp. 492.
